OL,4,Closing sight to go private
OL,6,FLong NHS waiting lists forced a woman
OL,7,Ffrom Hopkinstown, near Pontypridd, to
OL,8,Fseek a private diagnosis after being
OL,9,Ftold she had a serious eye condition.
OL,11,FBridie Doyle-Roberts was told by her
OL,12,Foptician that they suspected she had a
OL,13,Fdegenerative condition that would
OL,14,Faffect her eyesight.
OL,16,FShe was told not to drive home from
OL,17,Fthat appointment and was referred to
OL,18,Fhospital for confirmation of the
OL,19,Fcondition.
