OL,6,FHowever, she said to get this
OL,7,Fconfirmation she was added to a three
OL,8,Fyear waiting list.
OL,10,F"I felt like I couldn't wait" Bridie
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"Not knowing whether I could drive,
OL,14,Fnot knowing if I had the condition,
OL,15,Fhow it was going to affect me, what I
OL,16,Fcould do in terms of accessing
OL,17,Fsupport. There were so many questions
OL,18,Fwhich I had and I wanted the answers
OL,19,Fsooner."
