OL,6,F"I got support from some family
OL,7,Fmembers to pay for a private
OL,8,Fappointment to get an initial
OL,9,Fconsultation with an ophthalmologist
OL,10,Fto at least try and get some answers."
OL,12,FFollowing her private appointment,
OL,13,FBridie was referred back to the NHS to
OL,14,Fsee a genetic specialist, who she saw
OL,15,Ffour months later.
OL,17,F"I was really happy with the NHS
OL,18,Ftreatment but the waiting was a real
OL,19,Fchallenge.
