OL,6,FI would still be waiting now to be
OL,7,Fseen just to confirm with or not I
OL,8,Fhave this condition, which would have
OL,9,Fmeant I had missed out on the support
OL,10,FI have been getting over the last few
OL,11,Fyears."
OL,13,FNHS Wales data published on Thursday
OL,14,Fshows there are more than 8,000 two-
OL,15,Fyear waits to start treatment. This is
OL,16,Fa rise on the previous month.
OL,18,FThe number of people waiting for eye
OL,19,Ftreatment has dropped compared to the
OL,20,Fprevious month, with 105,559 waits in
OL,21,FJuly and 108,139 in June.
