OL,6,FBut the number of waits remains more
OL,7,Fthan double pre-pandemic levels.
OL,9,FHealth Secretary Jeremy Miles said an
OL,10,Fextra 15,000 outpatient appointments
OL,11,Fare being provided across Wales this
OL,12,Fmonth as part of plans to cut long
OL,13,Fwaiting times.
OL,15,FMore than 20,000 extra cataract
OL,16,Foperations will be provided by the end
OL,17,Fof March 2026 as part of the plan.
