OL,6,F"In July, there were an average of
OL,7,Fjust over 5,000 referrals for a first
OL,8,Foutpatient appointment a day, which is
OL,9,Fthe highest figure on record and
OL,10,Fdemonstrates the scale of demand for
OL,11,FNHS care.
OL,13,F"We are expecting to see fluctuations
OL,14,Fin the month-on-month statistics. I
OL,15,Fremain confident we will see a
OL,16,Fsignificant reduction in long waits by
OL,17,Fthe end of the second quarter."
